{UTF-8}
Income=Income Factor * Economic Growth
	~	
	~		|

Agricultural Land Requirement=Annual kcal production per km2 / Yield
	~	
	~	1.8e+09 kcal/km^2/Jahr repraesentiert die angenommene jaehrliche \
		Nahrungsenergieproduktion pro Quadratkilometer landwirtschaftlich \
		genutzter, getreidebasierter Produktionsflaeche in der EU.
		1.8e+09 kcal/km^2/Jahr ist ein cereal-basierter Proxy fuer die jaehrliche \
		Nahrungsenergieproduktion pro km^2, abgeleitet aus Eurostat-Daten zur \
		EU-Getreideproduktion 2023 und einer FAO-Kaloriendichte fuer Weizen.
		Eurostat: 271.6 Mio. t Getreideproduktion auf 51.0 Mio. ha geernteter \
		Getreideflaeche in der EU 2023.
		FAO: Weizen = 334 kcal pro 100 g als Kalorien-Proxy.
		
		Daraus folgt:
		
		271.6 Mio. t / 51.0 Mio. ha = 5.33 t/ha
		= 533 t/km^2
		533 × 3.34 Mio. kcal/t
		= ca. 1.78 × 10^9 kcal/km^2/Jahr.
	|

Ammount Large City=Urban Population Total * (Share Large City / Treshold Large City)
	~	
	~		|

Ammount Medium City=Urban Population Total * (Share Medium City / Treshold Medium City\
		)
	~	
	~		|

Ammount Small City=Urban Population Total * ( Share Small City / Treshold Small City)
	~	
	~		|

Ammount Very Large City=Urban Population Total * (Share very Large City / Treshold Very Large City\
		)
	~	
	~		|

Annual kcal production per km2=1.8e+06
	~	
	~		|

Max Ceiling Soil Protection=0.3
	~	
	~	Bedingung: 
		——————
		Wenn Urban Land nach multiplikation mit Spacial Planing und Soil Protection dreimal \
		grösser ist, als die Initial Urban Land, tritt dieser Effekt ein.
		——————
		Effekt: 
		Es stellt die Untere Schranke der Soil Protection Effect auf 0.3 \
		standardmässig ein.
	|

Economic Growth=Economic Growth Factor * Urban Land Index
	~	
	~		|

Economic Growth Factor=1.02
	~	
	~		|

Soil Protection Factor=1.001
	~	
	~		|

Spacial Planing Factor=1.0001
	~	
	~		|

Spatial Planning=Urban Land Index * Spacial Planing Factor
	~	
	~		|

Innovation very Large=Ammount Very Large City  * Treshold Very Large City^Urban Scaling Exponent very Large
	~	
	~		|

Income Factor=1.1
	~	
	~		|

Treshold Medium City=250000
	~	
	~		|

Innovation Large=Ammount Large City * Treshold Large City^Urban Scaling Exponent Large
	~	
	~		|

Innovation Medium=Ammount Medium City* Treshold Medium City^Urban Scaling Exponent Medium
	~	
	~		|

Innovation Small=Ammount Small City* Treshold Small City^Urban Scaling Exponent Small
	~	
	~		|

Urban Scaling Exponent very Large=2
	~	
	~		|

Urban Scaling Exponent Small=1.1
	~	
	~		|

Land Consumption Factor=1.0003
	~	
	~		|

Land Consumption per Capita=Land Consumption Factor * Income
	~	
	~		|

Land Conversion Pressure=MIN ( Land Conversion Pressure Factors, Aggricultural Land /\
		 1)
	~	
	~		|

Land Conversion Pressure Factors=(Land Consumption per Capita * 
	Economic Pressure * 
	Soil Protection Effect * 
	Agricultural Land Requirement)
	/1
	~	
	~		|

Treshold Very Large City=1e+06
	~	
	~		|

Soil Protection=Spatial Planning * Soil Protection Factor
	~	
	~		|

Treshold Small City=50000
	~	
	~		|

Treshold Large City=500000
	~	
	~		|

Soil Protection Effect=MAX(Max Ceiling Soil Protection, 1 / Soil Protection)
	~	
	~		|

Urban Scaling Exponent Medium=1.5
	~	
	~		|

Urban Scaling Exponent Large=1.7
	~	
	~		|

Aggricultural Land= INTEG (
	-Land Conversion Rate,
		1.6004e+06)
	~	km2 [0,?]
	~		|

Land Conversion Rate=
	MIN (Land Conversion Pressure, Max Feasible Conversion)
	~	km2/Time
	~		|

Max Feasible Conversion=
	Aggricultural Land / 1
	~	
	~		|

"Kcal per km^2 avg per t"=
	1.8e+09
	~	
	~		|

Reference Initial Urban Land= INITIAL(
	Urban Land)
	~	
	~		|

Urban Land Index=
	Urban Land / Reference Initial Urban Land
	~	
	~		|

Yield=
	"Kcal per km^2 avg per t" * (1+ Innovation Index)
	~	kcal / km2
	~	(Population * Pro person Bedarf) / Food Production
		
		Eurostat gibt fuer die EU 2023 eine Getreideproduktion von 271.6 Mio. t auf 51.0 \
		Mio. ha an. Das sind rund 5.33 t/ha. FAO gibt fuer Weizen grob 334 kcal \
		pro 100 g an, also etwa 3.34 Mio. kcal pro Tonne.
		
		
		es folgt: ≈ 1.8 Milliarden kcal pro km^2 und Jahr
	|

Share Medium City=
	0.07
	~	City
	~		|

Share Small City=
	0.85
	~	City
	~		|

Share very Large City=
	0.04
	~	City
	~		|

Share Large City=
	0.04
	~	City
	~		|

Total Urban Innovation Potential=
	(Innovation Large+Innovation Medium+Innovation Small + Innovation very Large)
	~	
	~		|

Innovation Index=
	Total Urban Innovation Potential / Reference Total Innovation Potential
	~	
	~		|

Urban Population Density=
	1500
	~	Person/km2
	~		|

Urban Population Total=
	Urban Land / Urban Population Density
	~	Person
	~		|

Reference Total Innovation Potential=
	INITIAL( Total Urban Innovation Potential )
	~	
	~		|

Economic Pressure=
	1 + (Import Dependence)^2
	~	
	~		|

Caloric Baseline Need pP=
	3400*365
	~	kcal / Person
	~	Ein EU-Kommissionsbericht, der sich auf FAO-Schaetzungen stuetzt, nennt \
		fuer die EU eine durchschnittliche dietary energy supply von 3’416 kcal \
		pro Person und Tag.
	|

Food Production=
	Yield *Aggricultural Land
	~	kcal
	~		|

Import Dependence=
	(Population*Caloric Baseline Need pP) / Food Production
	~	
	~		|

Urban Land= INTEG (
	Land Conversion Rate,
		181700)
	~	km2 [0,1.7821e+06]
	~		|

Population=4.5e+08
	~	
	~		|

